OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank of England sorry for  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frising cost of living      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England governor has said  
OL,6, he is "very sorry" that UK inflation is
OL,7, rising amid forecasts the cost of      
OL,8, living could reach as much as 5%.      
OL,10,FAndrew Bailey told the BBC that        
OL,11,Fhouseholds were already feeling the    
OL,12,Fimpact of rising prices.               
OL,14,F"I'm very sorry that's happening," he  
OL,15,Fsaid. "None of us want to see that     
OL,16,Fhappen."                               
OL,18,FOn Thursday, the Bank surprised        
OL,19,Ffinancial markets by voting to keep the
OL,20,Finterest rate unchanged.               
